PrecisAuthority to amend the CHAMPAGNE AND AISHIHIK FIRST NATIONS SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to empower them to enact laws relating to the implementation of measures made pursuant to any taxation agreement with the Minister of Finance and provide them with a GST refund paid by their government when performing its functions, effective November 1, 2000.

Authority to amend the CHAMPAGNE AND AISHIHIK FIRST NATIONS SELF-GOVERNMENT
AGREEMENT to empower them to enact laws relating to the implementation of
